Insider Activity


Individual




Juan Acosta-Reboyras



Mr. Juan Acosta-Reboyras, CPA, is Independent Director at First BanCorp (Puerto Rico), Partner at Acosta & Ramírez LLC, a Member at Puerto Rican Bar Association, Inc., a Member at American Bar Association, and a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. He is on the Board of Directors at First BanCorp (Puerto Rico) and FirstBank of Puerto Rico (Santurce, San Juan).
Mr. Acosta-Reboyras was previously employed as a Member by The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants.



